        "role": "user",
        "content": "Please review the book concept provided in the context and identify the following values as accurately as possible. Provide the response as a single, valid JSON object. Do not enclose the json in triple backticks.\n\nContext:\n{book_content}\n\nKeys required:\n'title'\n'subtitle'\n'author'\n'publisher'\n'imprint'\n'publication_date'\n'language'\n'bisac_codes' (provide 2-3 relevant BISAC codes as a semicolon-separated string)\n'series_name'\n'series_number'"
      }
    ],
    "tags": [
      "metadata",
      "json"
    ]
  },
